&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking a Civil Engineer to be based in Somerset or Greensburg, PA. In this role, you will gain hands-on experience supporting a diverse portfolio of land development projects, including private sector and municipal development. You’ll collaborate with experienced professionals who are committed to mentorship and fostering long-term career growth within a highly collaborative team environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Responsibilities as a Civil Engineer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform detailed civil engineering design for land development projects, including site layout, grading, stormwater management, erosion and sediment control, and utility design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support site feasibility studies, due diligence, and zoning/code compliance reviews for a variety of development projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and review design plans, technical specifications, cost estimates, calculations, and engineering reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with permitting and approvals, coordinating with local, state, and federal agencies and responding to agency comments&lt;/li&gt;
