&lt;li&gt;Participate in client, contractor, and municipal meetings, documenting key decisions and follow-up actions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support during construction, including reviewing submittals, responding to RFIs, and conducting site visits as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to proposal development, scope definition, and client presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate project documentation, budgets, and progress tracking within internal systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively pursue professional development opportunities, with a focus on advancing within land development engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
