&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Civil Engineering, Geotechnical Engineering, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;EIT required, PE preferred or on track&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience, with exposure to site design and land development projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with PADEP permitting processes and coordination is preferred.&lt;

