&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; Providing health and safety compliance auditing to the client
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn the client’s audit criteria, requirements, methods and culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete desktop work to include: reviewing site plans, completing client-designed checklists, attending team meetings as requested, and completing detailed timesheets and expense reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct site observations focused on identifying and assessing compliance with client-developed design requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate professional behaviors in service to the client and their stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;In collaboration with Apex project managers, coordinates and executes safety projects within set organizational procedures and standards.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; In close routine collaboration with the customer, designs, implements and executes an agreed-to service plan. Works with numerous internal and external stakeholders in the interest of achieving desired overall project velocity.&lt;/li&gt;
